            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Okay I tested it and it worked. So i think we can close my pr in favor of the https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/pull/4376.  \n\nFYI until it is merged, I am just overwriting the `before_init` method by using the current main branch and this file `/after/lsp/tailwindcss.lua`\n\n```lua\nlocal util = require(\"lspconfig.util\")\n\n---@type vim.lsp.Config\nreturn {\n\tbefore_init = function(_, config)\n\t\tconfig.settings = vim.tbl_deep_extend(\"keep\", config.settings, {\n\t\t\teditor = { tabSize = vim.lsp.util.get_effective_tabstop() },\n\t\t})\n\tend,\n}\n```",
