            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "> Do you know if it is efficient? (Ignoring node_modules)? Or at least async.\n\nI believe yes, [based on the implementation](https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-intellisense/blob/main/packages/tailwindcss-language-server/src/tw.ts#L334), it seems to be async using globs, search in parallel and [excludes ignored files](https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-intellisense#tailwindcssfilesexclude).\n\nIt's working pretty well, didn't have any issues with the automatic official detection.",
